title: Episode 222: Lip Service Live Tour NYC (Feat. Dasha Polanco, Chico Bean, Karlous Miller & Dave East)

description:
Dasha Polanco, Chico Bean, Karlous Miller & Dave East join the ladies for this special live show of Lip Service. Angela gives Dasha and the crew scenes to act out, as well as having Chico and Karlous freestyle for Dasha's love. Enjoy!
